*   [**Plane**](/Plane_(geometry)): A flat, two-dimensional surface extending infinitely.
*   [**Area**](/Area): The measure of the extent of a two-dimensional surface.
*   [**Polygon**](/Polygon): A closed two-dimensional figure made of straight line segments.

